src_id.name: src_id
src_id.description: Unique identifier for the economic event from the data source.

publish_datetime.name: publish_datetime
publish_datetime.description: The exact timestamp when the economic event is scheduled to be published (ISO 8601 format).

publish_date.name: publish_date
publish_date.description: The date when the economic event is scheduled to be published.

source.name: source
source.description: The source of the economic event data (e.g., Federal Reserve, BLS, ECB).

event_name.name: event_name
event_name.description: The name of the economic event (e.g., GDP Report, CPI Release, Interest Rate Decision).
